high_descs: Go right and enter the door on the left into the bedroom.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Go toward the bread on the bed.
Slice the bread with the knife.
Turn to the drawer on the left.
Place the knife in the bottom drawer of the bedstand.
Turn back to the bed.
Take one slice of bread from the loaf.
Exit the bedroom, then turn right and and enter the next door on the right, going towards the microwave.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and take it out.
Go towards the diningtable on the right.
Place the slice of bread on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a diningtable.

high_descs: Turn right then left to go into the bedroom, then approach the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Walk around the bed to the loaf of bread at the foot of it.
Slice the bread on the bed.
Turn to the drawers at the foot of the bed.
Place the knife in the drawer.
Turn back to the sliced bread.
Pick up one slice of the bread.
Exit this room, then turn right and right again immediately to get into another room, then approach the microwave in the far corner.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread and remove it.
Turn right to the dining table in this room.
Put the slice of bread down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a dining table.

high_descs: Move right and walk into the bedroom and face the bed.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Turn left to face the bottom of the bed.
Cut up the bread into slices on the bed with the knife.
Turn left to face the drawer.
Put the knife in the top drawer of the nightstand.
Turn right to face the bread on the bed.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Walk out the room and turn right to enter the dining room and walk to the microwave on the left.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and walk to the diningtable.
Put the slice of bread on the right side of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Bread on the DiningTable.
